================                          |  64%\n  |                                                                            \n  |=============================================                         |  64%\n  |                                                                            \n  |=============================================                         |  65%\n  |                                                                            \n  |==============================================                        |  65%\n  |                                                                            \n  |==============================================                        |  66%\n  |                                                                            \n  |===============================================                       |  66%\n  |                                                                            \n  |===============================================                       |  67%\n  |                                                                            \n  |===============================================                       |  68%\n  |                                                                            \n  |================================================                      |  68%\n  |                                                                            \n  |================================================                      |  69%\n  |                                                                            \n  |=================================================                     |  69%\n  |                                                                            \n  |=================================================                     |  70%\n  |                                                                            \n  |=================================================                     |  71%\n  |                                                                            \n  |==================================================                    |  71%\n  |                                                                            \n  |==================================================                    |  72%\n  |                                                                            \n  |===================================================                   |  72%\n  |                                                                            \n  |===================================================                   |  73%\n  |                                                                            \n  |===================================================                   |  74%\n  |                                                                            \n  |====================================================                  |  74%\n  |                                                                            \n  |====================================================                  |  75%\n  |                                                                            \n  |=====================================================                 |  75%\n  |                                                                            \n  |=====================================================                 |  76%\n  |                                                                            \n  |======================================================                |  76%\n  |                                                                            \n  |======================================================                |  77%\n  |                                                                            \n  |======================================================                |  78%\n  |                                                           